author: @heartsmile112
text: This is my favorite song in Self-Portrait. The first time I heard it, I cried. It really spoke to my soul. Suho's voice is so gentle and warm like a soft pillow. Younha's voice is like sunlight in a chilly morning. Their harmony is perfect. I saw an imagery of myself lying on a grassfield as I hear the sound of a stream nearby and the soft movements of grass as I listened. Everything was at peace. And when I read the lyrics, I never thought the song could be more beautiful than it already is. It was a lullaby. This song calms my heart as I prepare myself to have a good sleep. Thank you so much for this beautiful song, Suho. I miss you so much and I can't wait to see you sing again.

text: [D-625] You really know the way into our hearts! I'm sorry that we can't give you everything.. but we promise, I, promise to stay with you and support you while you are serving your country.. thank goodness that you are eating and sleeping well.. I am so proud of you leading a 159 comrades!!! How does it feel having a 159 son??? Hahaha is it also a disaster during free time? Hahahha.. thank you so much for the update.. I haven't even sent a letter to the camp.. thank you for thinking of iexols too.. please know that you are being loved, don't think too small about yourself.. thank you for all the good words to comfort us Junmyeon.. you really assured us that you are well, safe and happy.. omg I can't srop writing all my thoughts here, I need to stop... maybe you're resting now or sleeping.. you gave us a beautiful day today.. it's your birth month but uou're the one who gave us a gift.. thank you so much Junmyeon.. thank you... iloveyou No. 65 recruit Kim Junmyeon of 23rd regiment, 6th company, 2nd platoon, 1st squad! Salute! Goodnight! ^^ <3

author: @chyunazs
text:
Woah listening to this song makes me lost in thoughts. It put me into the image of a place where is very far away, there is no one there, I see huge fluffy clouds in the sky, and the breeze is strong yet chilling but I don't feel lonely. Instead, I am relaxing because in that place, I heard this song.

This song really can't be described by words. The way the harmonization created by Suho's and Younha's voices is undeniably perfect.
